               <p>Q. Do you know the person of the prisoner - A. I do not.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18131027-62-person666">
                  MARY 
                  ANN ROBERTSON
               <interp inst="t18131027-62-person666" type="surname" value="ANN ROBERTSON"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18131027-62-person666" type="given" value="MARY"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18131027-62-person666" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . Q. When did you become acquainted with the prisoner - A. About eight months previous to my being married to him. He addressed me as a single man. He was a carpenter. and builder.</p>
               <p>Q. When did you discover that he had a wife<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="181310270046"></xptr>living - A. It is three months since I discovered it, and since I discovered it I have ceased to live with him.</p>
               <p>
            
